{"tid":1750674,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"堅尼地城嘅街坊，求你地","createTime":"2019-11-24T13:05:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T13:10:45.000Z","uid":270308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c9277088b3d04e14f5baf5be878ca6c7332b105f","tid":1750674,"uid":270308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T13:05:33.000Z","msg":"民建聯張國均一定要輸，喺Physical門口，仲有老鼠成拉票。投左嘅落去幫3號拉票，或者幫手屌爆民建聯。求下你地"},{"pid":"462ccb6d53121ea05b57afcc84e302d9143f9ac2","tid":1750674,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T13:07:02.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咪撚做休息撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n投完票，贏輸都好，我地有新野做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">文宣方向：</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 有得一人一票，社會氣氛好左幾多？而且大家都相信投票，年青人到長者教出黎投，所以應該一人一票選特首。<br />\n<br />\n2.我地要將種票、票多過投票人、送禮各種唔公平現象比英美兩國知。<br />\n<br />\n3. Poly手足被困多日，要求警察撤退。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBe water be humble </span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"8c470a140bc356b620c982dee8c0afa8b661dcd2","tid":1750674,"uid":270308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T13:10:06.000Z","msg":"自推 x 1"},{"pid":"bb6a415d6de7722fd93d43789fb4da07f1978f3c","tid":1750674,"uid":270308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T13:10:31.000Z","msg":"自推 x 2"},{"pid":"0b8303b2f09eb5814f3a0c4ef436ede605db3507","tid":1750674,"uid":270308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T13:10:45.000Z","msg":"自推 x 3"}]}